{
  "stem": "16.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We traveled with my cousin Andy to every major city in, in Europe, I guess either to look for additional survivors.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were allowed to travel free of charge everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the only one I definitely heard about is, is my younger brother, who was with my cousin Andy--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the way he stayed alive-- remained alive-- one morning-- or one day, they picked him among 20 or 25 other people on a detail.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You, you, you, you-- come with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was taken outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a Warsaw, Warsaw camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother was inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and just as he was outside, working on some detail-- I don't know what they were doing, digging ditches or whatever-- the Polish people staged an uprising against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And shooting and chaos left and right-- and he quickly took, took off civilian clothes from a dead person.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He spoke good Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he just mingled in among the-- he lived the rest of the war out on a farm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The farmer probably suspected that he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he was doing his work just for the food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and, and he slept in the barn, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how he remained alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he told me also that my brother was inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody that was inside was either killed or-- they, they set the camp on fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so I know that my brother didn't make it that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But about my older brother, or the youngest brother, while I suspected they-- they had no use for seven-year-old kids, other than, God forbid, a, a, a lampshade.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe by some freak thing, maybe he's alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody saved him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We traveled all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
